746
00:32:21,956 --> 00:32:24,124
Well, why is someone
who is not your husband

747
00:32:24,208 --> 00:32:26,376
neck-deep in my fur?

748
00:32:26,460 --> 00:32:29,546
<i>-Can't answer that.</i>
-It's freezing in here.

749
00:32:29,630 --> 00:32:31,381
