750
00:32:31,465 --> 00:32:34,551
Sophie, I'm sorry, really,
but can I call you back later?

751
00:32:34,635 --> 00:32:36,345
-Where are you?
-At a USO show.

752
00:32:36,429 --> 00:32:38,764
<i>-I don't do USO shows.</i>
-It's not for you.

753
00:32:38,848 --> 00:32:40,098
