he gave me the clap.

761
00:32:58,993 --> 00:33:01,954
I'm sorry, about this and the clap.

762
00:33:02,038 --> 00:33:05,040
The clap was worth it. This isn't.

763
00:33:05,124 --> 00:33:08,752
<i>Now I have been patient,
