764
00:33:08,836 --> 00:33:12,422
I want an answer to my
question and I want it right now.

765
00:33:12,506 --> 00:33:17,219
Are you my manager or are you not?

766
00:33:17,303 --> 00:33:19,512
ABE: Rose, I don't understand why

767
00:33:19,596 --> 00:33:21,222
-[BANGING]
-What is that?

768
00:33:21,306 --> 00:33:23,516
-I demand you tell me exactly what you…
-[BANG]

769
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:25,685
