emotionally-retarded eunuchs
to draw symbols on a chalkboard.

787
00:34:07,978 --> 00:34:09,979
I think you're
oversimplifying my classes.

788
00:34:10,063 --> 00:34:12,690
Do you know one other
professor who lives the way we do?

789
00:34:12,774 --> 00:34:15,776
-Milk is 49 cents a gallon?
-Not one.

790
00:34:15,860 --> 00:34:18,945
They all have drab clothes
and gray skin and they die young.

791
00:34:19,029 --> 00:34:22,115
You're telling me that you
paid for all of these things

792
00:34:22,199 --> 00:34:23,950
