-Yes.

793
00:34:24,034 --> 00:34:26,036
You told me that trust
fund was just there

794
00:34:26,120 --> 00:34:27,245
to buy me birthday presents.

795
00:34:27,329 --> 00:34:28,580
Well, happy fucking birthday, Abe.

796
