801
00:34:40,718 --> 00:34:42,427
Who needs all these rooms?

802
00:34:42,511 --> 00:34:44,137
A living room, a dining room,

803
00:34:44,221 --> 00:34:46,431
a kitchen, two bathrooms.

804
00:34:46,515 --> 00:34:48,475
