magazines, planning menus.

876
00:37:15,579 --> 00:37:18,164
-And I had to sit with him all morning.
-I told you,

877
00:37:18,248 --> 00:37:20,708
-it wasn't right.
-Is it another man?

878
00:37:20,792 --> 00:37:22,210
-No. No.
-No?

879
00:37:22,294 --> 00:37:24,378
-No?
-Seriously, break the logjam.

880
00:37:27,298 --> 00:37:29,300
I'd follow her if I were you.

881
00:37:30,968 --> 00:37:32,803
MIDGE: Mama. Mama, can we please

882
