reason that you left Benjamin?

891
00:37:53,866 --> 00:37:55,742
-What? No.
-He sends you flowers.

892
00:37:55,826 --> 00:37:57,160
I am not spending the morning with him.

893
00:37:57,244 --> 00:37:58,453
You can tell him that right now.

894
00:37:58,537 --> 00:38:00,789
Will you listen to me?
I said he was just a friend.

895
00:38:00,873 --> 00:38:02,124
I can't believe you dropped a surgeon

896
00:38:02,208 --> 00:38:03,416
