00:38:56,928 --> 00:38:59,054
How dare you double-please me.

924
00:38:59,138 --> 00:39:01,265
You don't even know who Lenny Bruce is.

925
00:39:01,349 --> 00:39:03,809
You blather on and on about free speech.

926
00:39:03,893 --> 00:39:06,437
